## 5. TECHNICAL SPECIFICATIONS
- **Backend Framework**: Django 6.0 | Django REST Framework (DRF)
- **Frontend Layer**: ES2022 Vanilla JavaScript | Modern CSS with Variables
- **Database Architecture**: SQLite3 (Optimized for performance and concurrency)
- **Responsive Snap-points**: 768px (Mobile/Tablet transition), 1024px (Large Desktop)

---

## 6. FINAL VERIFICATION & HANDOVER
The Natdemy English App has passed a 360-degree audit. All historical bugs have been resolved, and the new features are verified as production-stable. The repository is clean, documented, and ready for immediate deployment.

